This plugin runs apuledctld on early startup before mounting root 
filesystem R/W. Also there are actions for manage apuledctld when
system startup done or reboot initiated.
apuledctld - a simple daemon for monitor of the button on front
panel of PCEngines APU<x> devices. By default, long press this
button performs reset opnsense configuration to default state.
Also it can control illumination of three LEDs on front panel.
